title: Qdoba company-owned restaurant sales from 2011 to 2018
summary: This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Sales in million U.S. dollars, with a total of 8 data points. The chart has 2 significant trends.
The longest trend is extremely positive which exists from 2017 to 2011.
Also, the next significant trend is slightly negative which exists from 2018 to 2017.
gold: This statistic shows the sales made by Qdoba company-owned restaurants from 2011 to 2018 . Qdoba , owned by Jack in the Box Inc. , generated restaurant sales of approximately 192.62 million U.S. dollars in 2018 .
